### Create user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice",
  "email": "alice@example.com"
}

### Create another user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob",
  "email": "bob@example.com"
}

### Get all users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users

### Get user by id — replace with an id from the create response
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{{userId}}

### Get user by unknown id — expect 404
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/non-existing-id
